onbury-2024-rumours-spread-of-secret-coldplay-show-at-local-venue-3769280">有人猜测酷玩乐队将在格拉斯顿伯里当地的一个场地举行秘密表演</a>。乐队即将在“值得农场”(Worthy Farm) 上亮相，歌迷们认为，在大型舞台卡车和乐队的装备出现在场馆后，他们可能会在弗罗姆的 Cheese &amp; Grain 进行一场热身表演。</p><p>然而， <a href="https://www.somersetlive.co.uk/whats-on/music-nightlife/coldplay-glastonbury-venue-rehearsal-music-9371951" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>SomersetLive</em></a>报道称乐队只是在那里排练。该场馆还发表了一份声明，透露：“我们收到了大量有关格拉斯顿伯里秘密演出在该场馆的潜力的询问。我们可以明确表示，在周日放映 2024 年欧洲杯英格兰 16 强比赛之前，Cheese &amp; Grain 不会举办任何活动。 </p><figure id="attachment_3518257" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3518257" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3518257" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BombayBicycleClub-header-image-Tom-Oxley-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3518257" class="wp-caption-text">孟买自行车俱乐部由 Tom Oxley 拍摄</figcaption></figure><p>“对于那些有幸在周末参加格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的人，我们希望您度过一段美好的时光并喝大量的水！”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bookies-odds-glastonbury-2024-secret-set-kasabian-kings-of-leon-pulp-3762814">整个周末，格拉斯顿伯里音乐节现场还有许多其他秘密演出</a>，卡萨比安有望填补周六伍西音乐节的待定席位。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-gates-to-glastonbury-2024-have-just-opened-3768713">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的大门已于昨天（6 月 26 日星期三）开放</a>，周末将有来自头条新闻<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA 等</a>音乐人的音乐表演，还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shania-twain-talks-glastonbury-2024-legends-slot-honour-of-my-life-3600979">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 的传奇老虎机</a>表演以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pj-harvey">PJ Harvey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">Burna</a>的表演。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">Boy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">Idles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anne-marie">Anne-Marie</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/confidence-man">Confidence Man</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/disclosure">Disclosure</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/camila-cabello">Camila Cabello</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">Avril Lavigne</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jessie-ware">Jessie Ware</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/masego">Masego</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sugababes">Sugababes</a>等等。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">在这里查看完整的阵容。</a></p><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/glastonbury-2024-set-clash-guide-3766391">以下是今年预计最严重的冲突</a>，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-weather-forecast-3763664">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的最新天气预报</a>。</p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024" target="_blank" rel="noope